source: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_SEQ_00<tab>Tsubame appears quite pleased with your progress.
target: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_SEQ_00<tab>ツバメは、冒険者に感心をしているようだ。

source: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_SEQ_01<tab>Tsubame is deeply impressed at the aptitude and affinity you have shown for the way of the shinobi, and she muses that your skills might one day rival her own. Now, the time has come to receive your next lesson. Enter the storehouse and speak with Oboro.
target: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_SEQ_01<tab>オボロが冒険者のことを待っているらしい。船着場の平屋の中にいる「オボロ」と話そう。

source: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_SEQ_02<tab>After proudly displaying his own mastery of a challenging technique─the common Eorzean bow─Oboro teaches you your second mudra. Known as <var 1A 02 /var>Chi<var 1A 01 /var> in the Doman tongue, this gesture will allow you to call forth the power of the earth itself. When you are prepared to learn how to wield it in battle, speak with Oboro once more.
target: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_SEQ_02<tab>オボロから新たな印、「地の印」を教えてもらった。修行の説明を聞くため、再度オボロに話しかけよう。

source: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_TSUBAME_000_000<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>! Why, I did not even hear your footsteps as you approached. You are becoming more and more the shinobi with each day.
target:
TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_TSUBAME_000_000<tab>おや、<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>様。
ふふふ、忍びの者として、たくましくなられましたね！

source: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_TSUBAME_000_001<tab>Oboro has been awaiting your return. Please, enter.
target:
TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_TSUBAME_000_001<tab>オボロ様が平屋でお待ちです。
どうぞ、お入りください。

source: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_OBORO_000_005<tab>Hand before the torso, bend at the hips... Presence of mind, presence of mind...
target: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_OBORO_000_005<tab>心を無にすれば……礼もうまくいくはず……。

source: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_TSUBAME_000_010<tab>The ease with which you have grasped the basics of our art is impressive, to say the least. Neglect not your training, and I can foresee the day when your skills rival my own.
target:
TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_TSUBAME_000_010<tab>ふふふ、たくましくなられましたね！
私なんて、すぐに抜かされてしまいそうです。

source: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_OBORO_000_020<tab>Ah, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. It is clear from the manner in which you carry yourself that you have been most diligent in your training.
target:
TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_OBORO_000_020<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>……腕を上げたようだな。
しかし、成長したのは、お主だけではござらぬぞ。

source: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_OBORO_000_021<tab>But you are not the only one who has mastered the technique imparted to you. Behold my Eorzean bow, perfect in balance and form!
target:
TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_OBORO_000_021<tab>見よ、この自然な礼を……。
日々の鍛錬を積んだ成果だ。
……さて、今度は、我々が修行を課す番だな。

source: TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_OBORO_000_022<tab>...Ahem. Now, it is time for your next lesson. Watch carefully my hands, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. With this mudra, the shinobi can summon the energies of the earth─<var 1A 02 /var>Chi<var 1A 01 /var>, in our tongue. Etch its form in your mind, and I shall show you how to employ it in battle.
target:
TEXT_JOBNIN350_00214_OBORO_000_022<tab>それでは、お主に新たな「印」……「地の印」を教える。
これは、大地に満ちるエーテルを結ぶ「印」だ。
後ほど、実戦を交えた修行を行うとしよう。
